headline: Palo Alto Networks Buys Chronosphere: Will Observability Fuel Growth?
summary: PANW's $3.35B deal for Chronosphere aims to boost observability for cloud and AI workloads by pairing its data with AgentiX's automation.

headline: Fiserv Appoints Walter Pritchard as Senior Vice President, Head of Investor Relations
summary: MILWAUKEE, December 01, 2025--Fiserv, Inc. (NASDAQ: FISV), a leading global provider of payments and financial technology, today announced the appointment of Walter Pritchard as Senior Vice President, Head of Investor Relations, effective December 1, 2025.
